data-copied-label="Copied!"
&gt;
&lt;div class="hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;OpenCode&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="opencode"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#opencode" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Add to &lt;code&gt;~/.config/opencode/opencode.json&lt;/code&gt; or your project &lt;code&gt;opencode.json&lt;/code&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code"&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-json" data-lang="json"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="nt"&gt;&amp;#34;mcp&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="nt"&gt;&amp;#34;cht-core-wiki&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="nt"&gt;&amp;#34;type&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34;remote&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="nt"&gt;&amp;#34;url&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34;https://opendeepwiki.dev.medicmobile.org/api/mcp?owner=medic&amp;amp;name=cht-core&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="nt"&gt;&amp;#34;enabled&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="kc"&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0"&gt;
&lt;button
class="hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50"
title="Copy code"
aria-label="Copy code"
data-copied-label="Copied!"
&gt;
&lt;div class="hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Available tools&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="available-tools"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#available-tools" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div class="hx:overflow-x-auto hx:mt-6 hx:flex hx:flex-col hx:rounded-lg hx:border hx:py-4 hx:px-4 hx:border-gray-200 hx:contrast-more:border-current hx:contrast-more:dark:border-current hx:border-green-200 hx:bg-green-100 hx:text-green-900 hx:dark:border-green-200/30 hx:dark:bg-green-900/30 hx:dark:text-green-200"&gt;
&lt;p class="hx:flex hx:items-center hx:font-medium"&gt;&lt;svg height=16px class="hx:inline-block hx:align-middle hx:mr-2" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;Tip&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="hx:w-full hx:min-w-0 hx:leading-7"&gt;
&lt;div class="hx:mt-6 hx:leading-7 hx:first:mt-0"&gt;&lt;p&gt;To guarantee a tool is invoked, explicitly name it in your prompt. For example: &lt;em&gt;&amp;ldquo;search_documents for &amp;lsquo;muting&amp;rsquo; in cht-core to understand how muted places affect contact form visibility&amp;rdquo;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Each repository endpoint exposes the same four tools:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th&gt;Tool&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th&gt;Purpose&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th&gt;Parameters&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/thead&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;get_document_catalog&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Get the table of contents for a repository&amp;rsquo;s generated wiki. Use this first to discover available documentation paths.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;owner&lt;/code&gt; (required), &lt;code&gt;name&lt;/code&gt; (required), &lt;code&gt;language&lt;/code&gt; (optional, default: &lt;code&gt;en&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;read_document&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Read a specific document from the generated wiki. Use &lt;code&gt;get_document_catalog&lt;/code&gt; first to find available paths.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;owner&lt;/code&gt; (required), &lt;code&gt;name&lt;/code&gt; (required), &lt;code&gt;path&lt;/code&gt; (required), &lt;code&gt;startLine&lt;/code&gt; (optional), &lt;code&gt;endLine&lt;/code&gt; (optional, max 200 lines), &lt;code&gt;language&lt;/code&gt; (optional)&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;search_documents&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Search across all generated documents in a repository for content matching a query. Returns matching document paths and snippets.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;owner&lt;/code&gt; (required), &lt;code&gt;name&lt;/code&gt; (required), &lt;code&gt;query&lt;/code&gt; (required), &lt;code&gt;language&lt;/code&gt; (optional)&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;list_repositories&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;List all repositories indexed by the OpenDeepWiki instance. Returns repository names, owners, and indexing status.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;None&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Recommended query patterns&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="recommended-query-patterns"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#recommended-query-patterns" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Discover structure first, then drill down:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;get_document_catalog&lt;/code&gt; — see the full table of contents&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;search_documents&lt;/code&gt; with your topic — find relevant pages&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;read_document&lt;/code&gt; on the specific path — get the detailed analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-repo investigation:&lt;/strong&gt;
When working on features that span repos, query multiple endpoints. For example, a configuration change might require searching &lt;code&gt;cht-conf-wiki&lt;/code&gt; for the compilation pipeline and &lt;code&gt;cht-core-wiki&lt;/code&gt; for the API endpoint that receives the upload.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Learn more&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="learn-more"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#learn-more" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The CHT Code Context MCP Server is part of the &lt;a href="https://github.com/medic/cht-agent" rel="external"&gt;CHT Agent&lt;/a&gt; multi-agent system for assisting in CHT development tasks. It serves as the &lt;strong&gt;Code Context Layer&lt;/strong&gt; in the Research Supervisor, complementing the Documentation Access Layer powered by the &lt;a href="https://docs.communityhealthtoolkit.org/ai/mcp-servers/cht-docs-mcp-server/"&gt;CHT Docs MCP Server&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Decision document&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;a href="https://github.com/medic/cht-agent/blob/main/designs/layer_recommendations/code-context-layer.md" rel="external"&gt;Code Context Layer Recommendation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OpenDeepWiki project&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;a href="https://github.com/AIDotNet/OpenDeepWiki" rel="external"&gt;github.com/AIDotNet/OpenDeepWiki&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>